div.div: Dungeon Meshi: Senshi no Kantan Cooking!

Stop-motion short in honor of the 5th tankoubon going on sale. It features Senshi's hands trying to prepare a walking mushroom. It is the same walking mushroom as shown in the manga's 1st volume in the "Monster Tidbits" bonus chapter.
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! MgRonald’s best demon lord worker is back, climbing the corporate ladder to become ruler of Earth. But Maou’s plans of domination might need to be put on hold when a small girl claims to be his and Emi’s child! (Source: Crunchyroll)

The story is about Ine and Shouzou, two pensioners well into their 80s who are mysteriously returned to their 20s one night. Note: Sixth place of Tsugimanga 2020 Award in the Web Manga Category Jiisan Baasan Wakagaeru is a web manga released on the author's pixiv and Twitter accounts, and later picked for print release by Kadokawa. Includes 4 extra chapters
Comedy, Drama, Romance, Slice of Life

"What am I doing?" Yuuhi Nagi's high school life is already halfway over, but he still doesn't have any dreams, ambitions, or even friends in his class! Every day is boring, until he's suddenly in danger of getting held back! A bittersweet high school drama made up of 4 potential grade repeaters with the worst grades in the class and 1 student acting as their teacher!
(Source: Pocket Comics)
